ShimeLinux is an unofficial Linux port/Kotlin rewrite of Shimeji-ee by Kilkakon
(https://kilkakon.com/shimeji). This project also incorporates work from
hqx-java by Arcnor (https://github.com/Arcnor/hqx-java) and FlatLaf by FormDev
(https://formdev.com/flatlaf).

